Title: Claude Shiny Chat
Type: Shiny
Author: CIMS Global
Description: A simple multi-turn chat application powered by Claude AI,
    built with R Shiny and the claudeAgentR SDK.
    claudeAgentR is available at https://github.com/Jimmy-CIMS/claude-code-sdk-r
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    shiny,
    bslib,
    shinyjs,
    promises,
    commonmark,
    claudeAgentR
